ComicInfo.Summary: Francine's information to Walsh that the senators new girlfriend is the woman she knew as Rachael and is in all probability a planted mole for the Parker group. Walsh calls a friend who works on a news paper looking for information and finds out that the last time they investigated the Parker's his wife was killed. Freddie claims to have lost the items of Francine that Chuck gave him and Francine thinks about telling Casey, but decides against it. Walsh phones her and tells her he's going unofficially to L.A. to look into the case for Francine. Darcy makes it plain to Katchoo she wants to control the whitehouse and Veronica will be the first lady and enable them to do just that... and whats more the current first lady is theirs too. All she needs is a distraction and Katina can do that for her. Katchoo agrees to do one job for Darcy, she recalls how callously she kills those who fail or disappoint her, she has to meet the head of the senate investigation committee studying organised crime in New York.
ComicInfo.Title: Suddenly
